Minimum 3 years related experience      on lab electrical test, background on soldering and manual welding on      electronic components are preferred.  专科以上学历，机械或电气相关领域，至少三年以上实验室电气测试经验，有电子元器件手工焊接经验优先。  Ability to understand IEC/ISO test standard and technical documents.  能理解IEC/ISO相关的测试标准及技术文件。  Knowledge of Lab test flow and test equipment specification.  了解实验室测试流程和常用测试设备技术规格。   Proven strong practical ability and experience of the test sample      preparation and test machine operation.   熟练的测试样品准备和设备操作技能。  Self-motivated and accountable.  有上进心和责任心。  Good interpersonal and communication and negotiation skills. Good      time management skills.  良好的人际交往和沟通能力及时间管理能力。  Basic English in reading and writing.  基本的英语读写能力。
